Requires RasPiCam:
https://github.com/cedricve/raspicam

Compile with:
g++ ml_server.cpp -o ml_server -I/usr/local/include -lraspicam

Code that is respnsible for communication with python program is wrapped around by 
// GSC - START/END

Set ENABLE_ML to enable machine learning.
(When disabled, this server will send randomly generated pseudo result to client)